# CODEOWNERS — Dark Factory Governance Platform (ai-submodule)
#
# Defines code ownership for pull request review requirements.
# The org ruleset "Pull Request - Reviewer" enforces require_code_owner_review.
#
# github-actions[bot] is included as a code owner so the Dark Factory governance
# workflow approval satisfies the code owner review requirement for auto-merge.
# This is specific to the ai-submodule repo. Consuming repos should configure
# their own CODEOWNERS via init.sh / project.yaml.

# Default owner — all files not matched by more specific rules
* @SET-Apps/approvers @github-actions[bot]

# CI/CD workflows require DevOps review
/.github/workflows/ @SET-Apps/devops_engineers @github-actions[bot]

# Infrastructure files require DevOps review
/infra/ @SET-Apps/devops_engineers @github-actions[bot]

# Governance submodule changes
/.ai @SET-Apps/approvers @github-actions[bot]
